      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;のフニャフニャ、
やわらかいのが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Rody&gt;'s bouncing things were so soft...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_060_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……何、ぽーっとしてるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...What are you daydreaming for?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_060_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>………………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ooh...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43116</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_060_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いちっ……何すんだよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ow! Hey what did I do now!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_060_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぼーっとしてたら、危ないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Keep daydreaming and it could be dangerous.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43284</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_060_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だからって殴るかよ、
このゴツゴツ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You are just mad because yours are plain!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
